{"tid":1014504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費托離港拒再簽名：我已幫你們簽過了","createTime":"2019-02-09T08:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T09:15:57.000Z","uid":216392,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5cb717ef509bd32a475e3454aaf2955660d1a0","tid":1014504,"uid":216392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"賀歲盃亞軍球隊鳥棲砂岩今日離港，約20名球迷到機場送機，惟陣中球星費蘭度托利斯婉拒球迷簽名要求，寄存行李後就直接進入禁區。<br />\n<br />\n周四完成賀歲盃後，鳥棲砂岩沒有立即離港，而是逗留多兩晚後，今晨才返回日本。約20名球迷一早到機場送機，托利斯當然是大部份球迷的目標，但球迷在寄存行李櫃位外一直等候，卻未能得到托利斯停下腳步，這位西班牙金童認出多位球迷是連日來的熟悉面孔，拋下一句：「我已經向你們全部都簽過名了。」就直接去到禁區。至於其他球員如豐田陽平等則有停下來為球迷簽名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190209/59239342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190209%2F59239342&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=d3af6a81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190209%2F59239342&h=70be17f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190209/59239342</a>"},{"pid":"8bb14bd13af2b1f9a8c7cc6d434c571b870c0827","tid":1014504,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3267e0e547656e21fbf4d2f37e2189cff45f7726","tid":1014504,"uid":26451,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b53fdcd4ee818e5824229dfafce3fe20085f6a9f","tid":1014504,"uid":39622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ffc2ce1aa7956721d85d41521978d2467d61c5","tid":1014504,"uid":39622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3267e0e547656e21fbf4d2f37e2189cff45f7726","ti